text: Graham Taylor (May 2, 1851 – September 26, 1938) was a Minister, Social Reformer, Chicago Theological Seminary faculty member, Educator and Founder of Chicago Commons Settlement House along with Jane Addams. ==References== *Graham Taylor at Social Welfare History *The Graham Taylor collection at the Newberry Library Category:1851 births Category:1938 deaths Category:American theologians Category:American sociologists
title: Graham Taylor (theologian)
